<recipe xmlns="https://cazzscookingcommunity.github.io" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <title>Mango Slushie</title>
  <filename>mango_slushie.xml</filename>
  <thumbnail>mango_slushie.jpeg</thumbnail>
  <category>Drink</category>
  <ingredient>1 cup frozen mango pieces</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1 cup cold jasmine tea</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Mint leaves</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Frozen lime slices </ingredient>
  <step>Wiz tea and mango in blender until done.</step>
  <step>Pour into Long glass or two smaller glasses, and garnish with lime and mint.</step>
  <step>Serve immediately.</step>
  <step>You can sweeten with honey if desired.</step>
</recipe>
